# Color Schemes Generator

Color generate for get schemes color

## Install

```
npm install color-schemes-generator

```

## Quickstart

```
const color = require("color-schemes-generator");

console.log(color.generate());
// Output: [ '#2D3E50', '#01C26E', '#F3C40F', '#E24C3F', '#8F44AB' ]
```
